pregnant to birth in 90 seconds touching time-lapse video shows how mother-to-be changes over timeby marcus barnes published 14 03 gmt 11 march 2012 14 23 gmt 11 march 2012 a_woman and_her partner spent nine months working on a_video project to document her pregnancy with heartwarming results their time lapse video simply called introducing shows her midriff grow from rather_toned and_flat belly to an_oversized protrusion towards the end of_her pregnancy_and finally the arrival of_their beautiful baby girl the well-produced video condenses the whole nine-month experience into just 90 seconds figure there she is the couple pose with their baby daughter after putting together an_epic nine-month video project kiss of_life the partner kneels down to plant his lips on her belly at the beginning of_the video it begins with the woman standing up waiting for her partner who enters the_room and_plants kiss on her flat tummy they then high-five each other presumably rather innocent way to illustrate the conception of_their baby girl when he leaves the room she turns to the_camera and_points at her stomach figure box clever midway through the video the couple move house presumably to gain extra space for their forthcoming arrival growth spurt the belly begins to get bigger in their new home_we then see time lapsed set of_scenarios as her stomach_grows and_their pet_cats and dogs_disappear and_reappear in the room around her at one point the couple move house at which time the partner picks her_up and_carries her across the threshold of_their new abode he then_disappears and_leaves her to continue to grow figures nearly there the tummy continues to_grow entering the final stages of_the pregnancy lip service the couple kiss in the final section of_the video finally when she appears about ready to_pop he returns once more she signals at her watch that time for someone new to join_them again getting down on his knees the_man kisses the belly this time however as he kisses her their baby daughter pops out figure special delivery the_man prepares to bring his daughter into the_world then they bring her closer to the camera for her first ever close_up and_her name amelie amaya flashes up on the screen youtube users have been quick to commend the couple for their nine-month long project one user named alfacinhotube wrote beautiful a_well-conceived wonderfully executed documentation of_a magnificent moment in your lives thanks for sharing a_girl amelie amaya is introduced to the world while woman with the user name malleolust said months pregnant with my first_child a_son this made me cry can blame hormones little amelie be blessed and_even one male viewer said the video brought him to_tears matstrick wrote beautiful you just brought
